para_trans: Funny Dhodup, Ta. Chikhli, G. Buldhana
Approval to set up a hospital
Government Decision, No: Establishment-2024 / P.No.70 / Health 3
Read: Letter from the Commissionerate of Health Services, Mumbai by No. / Room 3 / T-2 / No. 2408 / Sh.
Funny Dhodup, Ta. A proposal to set up a new 30-bed rural hospital at Chikhali, District Buldhana was under consideration of the government.
Funny Dhodup, Ta. Setting up of a new 30 bedded rural hospital at Chikhali, District Buldhana
It is being approved under this government decision as a "special matter" to be done. Sadar Rural
Separate action will be taken on the acquisition of land for the hospital in the prescribed manner for construction and post creation.
The decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra's www.maharashtra.gov.in website.
